&lt;Sumitomo Metal Industries Ltd> has set uptwo finance firms, one in Osaka and one in London, a companyspokesman said.    &lt;Sumitomo Metal International Finance Plc> in London iswholly-owned. &lt;Fuso Finance Co Ltd> in Osaka, is owned 50 pctby Sumitomo with the rest equally shared by two small SumitomoMetal subsidiaries.    The two new companies will work for the Sumitomo Metalgroup on fund raising and investment in financial markets. REUTER&#3;